 pf-222_">Can using a massage gun for cellulite treatment replace exercise and a healthy diet?</span></h3><p class="sc-lcepkR datYlM pf-223_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">No. In fact, one of the key benefits of using a massage gun is that it helps with your range of motion during exercise. Ultimately, the best way to address cellulite is by combining exercise and a healthy diet with regular massage and skin-boosting topical treatments.&nbsp;</p><div class="sc-cTAqQK cFxQA-d pf-225_ pf-r pf-r-eh pf-hide" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-1875" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-ihINtW bFPXVO pf-226_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-fvpsdx hSLMtg"><div class="sc-cTAqQK cFxQA-d pf-227_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-2627" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-ihINtW bFPXVO pf-228_ pf-hide"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-fvpsdx hSLMtg"><div class="sc-cTAqQK cFxQA-d pf-229_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-kjOQFR ctEqvM pf-230_"><div class="sc-cTAqQK cFxQA-d pf-231_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-kjOQFR ctEqvM pf-232_"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:8"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-kjOQFR ctEqvM pf-233_"><div class="sc-cTAqQK cFxQA-d pf-234_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:3"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-kjOQFR ctEqvM pf-235_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0621/2272/1446/t/26/assets/avatar1146e09cf01a5205043db6a6499887c1-1677185916858.jpg?v=1677185919" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0621/2272/1446/t/26/asse